This place serves some really good bubble tea. The flavours will pop in your mouth!
The ice tea is really bad though. I would suggest not to try it.
The ice-creams and cold coffee are good.
The variety in the menu is nice.

Will not recommend. Drinks are all flavoured and sugary on top of that they have to put Nitrogen. Fruit ice creams hardly had any fruits.
They served 10 people in 1 hour and that too we ordered only 10 items.
I ordered veg sandwich on Nourish, which was stuffed too less and was served cold.. bread was too hard to chew.
